product.name: Large Bilayer Acoustic Panels,6 Pack Sound Absorbing Panels,48” x 24” x 0.72” Sound Proof Panels for Walls,High-Density Acoustic Wall Panels,Decorative Sound Panels,Black
product.bullet_points:
• Dual-Layer Design - Features 48"x24" acoustic panels boasting a 0.72" dual-layer acoustic core. It utilizes sound wave diffusion technology for full-spectrum absorption, achieving 30% higher mid-to-high frequency noise elimination than single-layer alternatives—while using 25% less material. Acoustic wall panels delivers industry-leading noise cancellation in expansive spaces.
• 100% Premium Polyester Fiber - Soundproofing panels are crafted from entirely eco-friendly, odorless polyester fiber with zero harmful additives. Sound proof panels for walls features inherent flame resistance, along with enhanced moisture protection, mold prevention, and flexibility in precision cutting. Sound dampening panels combines lightweight durability with unmatched stability and cost efficiency.
• Aesthetic Enhancement - Premium felt-laminated acoustic panels sound absorbing feature sleek vertical striping that transforms walls into sophisticated decor. Available in classic white, Silver Grey, black, and Light Camel, sound proof panels for walls seamlessly blend into any environment while elevating its aesthetic appeal.
• Versatile Applications - Ideal for residential and commercial use: Enhance focus in home offices, optimize acoustics in conference rooms and recording studios, and craft immersive retail experiences. These bilayer acoustic panels not only block outside noise but also blend seamlessly with lighting and decor, creating a unique atmosphere.
• Installation - The noise dampening panels include double-sided acrylic adhesive for easy setup. For added security, we recommend using construction adhesive or nails. Their felt wall tiles feature precise edges, ensuring seamless installation.
